org.youscope.plugin.outoffocus

Interface OutOfFocusJob

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, ImageProducer, Job, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface OutOfFocusJob
extends Job, ImageProducer
    A job which makes a microscope image in the defined channel with a defined focus offset.
    Author:
    langmo
